comment_data.body:
Was a breakpoint by any chance hit when you restarted the application?
We recently fixed some cases where you would get timeout exceptions if a breakpoint was hit.

Hi @jacob314 - I have lost the track of bug, it's a way too old bug for me to hold and review again.

I will update my flutter, intellij today and will report in the future When I get a similar error again.

/closing it for now.
